tyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>todos<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span>los documentos<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.8pt''> </span>a<span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>suscribir,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> </span>(ii) los<span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>\r\n</span>cargos,<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> </span>el<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.2pt''> </span>monto de las<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.15pt''> </span>tasas<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> </span>de intereses<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> </span>y<span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>comisiones<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> </span>vigentes<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>\r\n</span>que<span style=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span>cobra por<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span>cada uno de los<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.15pt''> </span>conceptos<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> </span>previstos\r\nque<span style=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span>se establecen<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>el<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>presente<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''>\r\n</span>Contrato,<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>(iii)<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>su<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>caso,<span style=''letter-spacing:.4pt''> </span>los<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>descuentos<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.55pt''> </span>y<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>bonificaciones<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>que<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>en<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>su<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>caso<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>pudiera<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>tener<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>derecho,<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''>\r\n</span>y<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>(iv)<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.45pt''> </span>que<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>en caso<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>terminación<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>o<span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>baja<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:2.15pt''> </span>laboral<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>\r\n</span>con su<span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>actual<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> </span>Patrón,<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>\r\no que en caso de que por cualquier razón el patrón de </span><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> no logre retener el pago\r\npara depósito a CREA, o que CREA no de por recibido el pago de EL\r\nACREDITADO<span style=''mso-spacerun:yes''>  </span>a través del patrón a su <span\r\nclass=SpellE>enetera</span> satisfacción, seguirá siendo obligación de EL\r\nACREDITADO realizar los pagos correspondientes a este contrato, en el domicilio\r\nseñalado por CREA para objetos del presente contrato.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>CREA<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.1pt''> </span>DECLARA<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>LO</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>SIGUIENTE:<span\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:bold''><o:p></o:p></span><