ing:-.05pt''>Escritura</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>Pública</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.75pt''> </span>No.<span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>122,166,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>fecha<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>19</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>abril</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>2007,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> p</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>asada</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>ante<span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>la<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>fe<span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>del<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:3.05pt;mso-font-width:101%''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>Notario</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''>\r\n</span>Público<span style=''letter-spacing:1.25pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>No.</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.6pt''> </span>152<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>del<span style=''letter-spacing:1.6pt''> </span>Distrito<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>Federal,<span style=''letter-spacing:.65pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>Lic.</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.35pt''> </span>Cecilio<span style=''letter-spacing:1.5pt''> </span>Gonzales<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.3pt''> </span>Márquez, e inscrita en el Registro Público\r\nde Comercio con el Folio Mercantil No. 363745, de fecha 9 de Mayo de 2007;<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>manifestando<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>bajo</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>protesta</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.55pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>decir</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:5.25pt;mso-font-width:101%''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>verdad,</span> <span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>que</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>hasta la <span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>fecha,</span>\r\n<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>no</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''>\r\n</span>le<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt''>han</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span>sido<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span>revocadas<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>\r\nni</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>limitadas<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>sus<span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>facultades<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>forma</span> alguna.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>3.-</span></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.35pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span></b><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.35pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Su\r\ndomicilio fiscal y el domicilio asentado para cualquier tema relacionado para\r\nefectos del presente contrato, se encuentra ubicado</span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.3pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> en Boulevard\r\nAdolfo Ruiz Cortines 4302 Interior 212, Colonia Jardines Del Pedregal De San\r\nÁngel, Delegación Coyoacán, Ciudad De México C.P. 04500 <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>4.-</span></b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span class=GramE><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:.35pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Que</span></span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.35pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> en su\r\nobjeto social, entre otros, contempla la facultad de otorgar créditos.</span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>5.-</span></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span></b><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Que<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.15pt''> </span>considerando<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>las<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>declaraciones<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.55pt''> </span>de <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span>es<span style=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>su<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>voluntad<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>otorgar</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>un</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.35pt''> </span>crédito<span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>simple</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>con<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>interés.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>6.-</span></b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> Que no requiere de autorización por parte de la\r\nSecretaría de Hacienda y Crédito Público para su constitución y operación como\r\nsociedad financiera de objeto múltiple, y se encuentra sujeta a la inspección y\r\nvigilancia de la Comisión Nacional Bancaria y de Valores, pero exclusivamente\r\npara verificar el cumplimiento de las disposiciones preventivas de lavado de\r\ndinero y financiamiento al terrorismo (Art. 95-Bis de la Ley General de Organizaciones\r\ny Actividades Auxiliares del Crédito).</span><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\ncolor:#666666;background:white;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>7.</span></b><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>- <span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt''>Que el presente Contrato fue inscrito ante el Registro de Contratos de\r\nAdhesión de la Comisión Nacional para la Defensa de los Usuarios de los\r\nServicios Financieros, bajo el folio número: RECA: 1735-140-027143/02-06015-1117</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Expuestas<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>las<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>anteriores<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.3pt''> </span>declaraciones,<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>las<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>partes<span style=''letter-spacing:.6pt''> </span>que<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>suscriben<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>el</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.4pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>presente</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>contrato<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''>\r\n</span>manifiestan<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>su</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>voluntad<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>otorgar</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:5.35pt;mso-font-width:101%''> </span>y<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>sujetarse<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>al</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.15pt''> </span>tenor <span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>las<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>siguientes:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style=''text-align:center''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><u><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>CLÁUSULAS<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style=''text-align:center''><b><u><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p><span style=''text-decoration:\r\n none''> </span></o:p></span></u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>PRIMERA.<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.6pt''> </span><u style=''text-underline:black''>OBJETO<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.55pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>DEL</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.5pt''> </span>CONTRATO</u>.-<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.35pt''> </span></span></b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Sujeto\r\na la firma del “Consentimiento de Retención”, CREA, otorga a EL ACREDITADO, un\r\ncrédito simple con interés vía descuento de nómina, en moneda nacional (en lo\r\nsucesivo EL CRÉDITO SIMPLE), por un importe equivalente a $_______________\r\n(monto en letra). La citada cantidad, no comprende los intereses ordinarios,\r\ncomisiones e impuestos y demás gastos que deba cubrir el cliente a favor de\r\nCREA de acuerdo a éste contrato.<span style=''letter-spacing:1.35pt''><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:1.35pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>EL cliente dispondrá de la totalidad del crédito en\r\nuna sola exhibición, mediante dispersión automática de fondos en cualquier\r\nbanco que elija CREA, del cual EL ACREDITADO, se dará por recibido en la fecha\r\nque CREA abone a dicha cuenta. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>En caso de que el crédito sea destinado para una\r\nreestructuración de deuda, CREA podrá total o parcialmente transferir los\r\nrecursos a una tercera persona con la que EL ACREDITADO tenga un adeudo\r\nvigente. Para lo cual, CREA dispondrá de un comprobante de pago del adeudo. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;letter-spacing:-.05pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>SEGUNDA.</span></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nletter-spacing:1.6pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><u style=''text-underline:black''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>LUGAR<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> </span>Y<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>FORMA<span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>DE</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>PAGO</span></span></u></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>.-</span></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span></b><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>EL ACREDITADO</span></b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:\r\n.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>se<span style=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>obliga<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>a<span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>pagar:</span></span><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>La</span><span style=''font-size:\r\n8.0pt;letter-spacing:.25pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>cantidad<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.3pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>señalada</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>la<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>cláusula<span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''>\r\n</span>primera, los intereses ordinarios e intereses moratorios que se generen\r\nen virtud de lo pactado en el presente contrato, así como el Impuesto al Valor\r\nAgregado o cualquier impuesto que se encuentre vigente a la fecha en que se\r\ngenere por causación de intereses u otros gastos. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>EL ACREDITADO</span></b><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> se obliga a pagar a <b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b>, de acuerdo a las obligaciones\r\nderivadas del presente Contrato, las cantidades convenidas sobre el Crédito\r\nSimple, las cuales se pagarán de su salario en forma quincenal de conformidad\r\ncon el número de abonos y en los plazos estipulados en el “Consentimiento de\r\nRetención” que <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> solicite\r\na su Patrón, documento que se agregará al presente Contrato y es parte integrante\r\ndel mismo.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Si por cualquier razón, el pago de la parcialidad no\r\nla pudo realizar el Patrón por cuenta y orden de <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''>EL ACREDITADO</b>, <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b>\r\nse compromete a pagar los abonos en el domicilio señalado por CREA, según los\r\nplazos estipulados en la Carátula del Contrato; o bien, <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> ofrecerá su consentimiento, para que se realice la\r\ndomiciliación de dicho pago a la cuenta que el mismo proporcionó a <b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b> para tal efecto.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Para el caso de que, por cualquier razón, el pago de\r\nla parcialidad por parte del Patrón por cuenta y orden de <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> se llegase a realizar por una cantidad menor a la\r\nconvenida, se realice con un desfase mayor a 30 días naturales a la fecha en\r\nque corresponde cada amortización del crédito, o no se llegase a realizar por\r\ncompleto, en este acto <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b>,\r\nmanifiesta su conformidad para ampliar el número de abonos del presente\r\nContrato, hasta en tanto, el saldo insoluto quede totalmente amortizado.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>En<span style=''letter-spacing:.75pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>caso</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span>de<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.7pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>que</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.7pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>el</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span>día<span style=''letter-spacing:.6pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>en</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.75pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>que</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.6pt''> </span><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>EL\r\nACREDITADO</span></b><span style=''letter-spacing:.8pt''> </span>deba<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.7pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>efectuar</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.7pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>cualquier</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.75pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>pago,</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.9pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>fuere</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.7pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>día</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.7pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>inhábil,</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.8pt''> </span>dicho<span style=''letter-spacing:.75pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>pago</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.75pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>se</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.7pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>realizará</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.7pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>el</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.65pt''> </span>día<span style=''letter-spacing:.6pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>hábil</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.8pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>inmediato</span><span style=''letter-spacing:2.25pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>posterior</span> <span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>al</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>vencimiento</span> <span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt''>correspondiente, </span>lo <span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>anterior</span>\r\n<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>sin</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>que</span> <span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt''>proceda</span> el<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> cobro</span> de <span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>comisiones</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.15pt''> </span>o <span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>intereses</span> <span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>moratorios<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>TERCERA. <u>CONSENTIMIENTO\r\nDE RETENCIÓN.-</u> EL ACREDITADO </span></b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>en este acto acepta que mantendrá vigente el “Consentimiento\r\nde Retención” presentado al Patrón hasta que se cubran con el descuento a su\r\nnómina el total del crédito otorgado por <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b>\r\nmás sus accesorios.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>EL ACREDITADO</span></b><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> acepta que la Instrucción de\r\nPago del crédito y sus accesorios vía el descuento de nómina de <b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> sólo será suspendida\r\nhasta que el PATRÓN reciba un Aviso de parte de <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''>CREA</b> donde se confirme al PATRÓN que <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> ha pagado el préstamo otorgado y sus accesorios en su\r\ntotalidad.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>En caso de que <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL\r\nACREDITADO</b> incumpla con lo estipulado en esta cláusula y solicite al Patrón\r\ndejar sin efectos los pagos correspondientes del descuento de su crédito de\r\nnómina conforme a lo estipulado en el “Consentimiento de retención” que entregó\r\na su Patrón, <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> acepta\r\nque su patrón solo podrá llevar a cabo dicha solicitud una vez que reciba la\r\nsolicitud o instrucción de parte de <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b>,\r\ndonde se indique que los adeudos de <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL\r\nACREDITADO</b> han sido pagados en su totalidad. En caso de que <b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> tenga un saldo por\r\ncubrir, <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b> informará al patrón el\r\nadeudo que <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> tiene de su\r\npréstamo de nómina, y le indicará que la Instrucción de Pago deja de tener\r\nefecto hasta que quede cubierto dicho adeudo.<b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>CUARTA.<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span><u style=''text-underline:black''>INTERÉS<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>ORDINARIO</u><u>.-</u><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span></span></b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Las<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>partes<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>acuerdan<span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>que</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>la<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>cantidad</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.6pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>la<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>cláusula</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''>\r\n</span>primera<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>se</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.6pt''> </span>le<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>aplicará</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>por</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>concepto <span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>interés</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>ordinario<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''>\r\n</span>una tasa fija del<u style=''text-underline:black''><span style=''mso-tab-count:\r\n1''>                </span></u><span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''>(<u\r\nstyle=''text-underline:black''><span style=''mso-tab-count:1''>               </span></u></span>_)<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>en términos anuales<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt''>.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Los</span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.25pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>intereses</span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.35pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>que<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.3pt''> </span>se<span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>generen</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>con<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>motivo<span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>del</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>presente<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>contrato,<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''>\r\n</span>deberán<span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>ser<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>pagados<span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>por</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.4pt''> </span>dentro<span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>del<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>día<span style=''letter-spacing:3.75pt;\r\nmso-font-width:101%''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>hábil</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.8pt''> </span>inmediato<span style=''letter-spacing:1.0pt''>\r\n</span>siguiente<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>a<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span>la<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>semana<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>transcurrida,<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.9pt''> </span>y<span style=''letter-spacing:.9pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>por</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>la<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>que</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.8pt''> </span>se<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>generó<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>dicho<span style=''letter-spacing:1.0pt''> </span>interés,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.9pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>mientras</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>el</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.0pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''>saldo</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.0pt''> </span>del<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>capital\r\n<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>señalado</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.1pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>la<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span>cláusula<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''>\r\n</span>primera<span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span>se<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>encuentre<span style=''letter-spacing:.15pt''>\r\n</span>insoluto.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Los</span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.3pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>intereses</span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.3pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>se<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.35pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>devengarán</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>por</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>quincenas</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>vencidas,</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>según</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>sea</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>el</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>caso,</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>a<span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>partir</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>la<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>fecha</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>disposición</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:3.95pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>del</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.75pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>Crédito</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.7pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>Simple.</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.8pt''> </span>El<span style=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>cálculo</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.75pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.6pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>intereses</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span>se<span style=''letter-spacing:.7pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>realizará</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.6pt''>\r\nde forma </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>quincenal,</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span>multiplicando<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.6pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>el</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span>saldo<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>insoluto<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.6pt''> </span>del<span style=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span>Crédito<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:4.35pt''> </span>simple<span style=''letter-spacing:1.3pt''>\r\n</span>por<span style=''letter-spacing:1.3pt''> </span>la<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.25pt''> </span>tasa<span style=''letter-spacing:1.3pt''> </span>de<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.35pt''> </span>interés<span style=''letter-spacing:1.35pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>mencionada al inicio de la presente\r\ncláusula.</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.4pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>El</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.35pt''> </span>resultado<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>así<span style=''letter-spacing:1.25pt''> </span>obtenido,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>se<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>dividirá</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''>\r\n</span>entre<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt''>360</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.35pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>(trescientos</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.25pt''> </span>sesenta)<span style=''letter-spacing:1.7pt''> </span>días<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.35pt''> </span>y,<span style=''letter-spacing:1.4pt''> </span>a<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>su<span style=''letter-spacing:1.35pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>vez,</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.35pt''> </span>dicho<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.45pt''> </span>resultado<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.15pt''> </span>se<span style=''letter-spacing:4.9pt''> </span>multiplicará<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>por<span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>\r\n_____<span class=GramE>_(</span>15, o de acuerdo a la periodicidad pactada en\r\nel pago de las amortizaciones). <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.15pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.15pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>En caso de que, conforme a la\r\nLey del Impuesto al Valor Agregado, EL ACREDITADO deba pagar <span\r\nstyle=''mso-spacerun:yes''> </span>tal impuesto, o cualquier otro que a la fecha\r\nse encuentre vigente, deberán ser pagados a CREA conjuntamente con los\r\nintereses ordinarios generados.</span><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>El </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>pago<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.2pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>los</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span>intereses<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>no<span style=''letter-spacing:-.2pt''> </span>podrá\r\n<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>ser</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.2pt''>\r\n</span>exigido por <span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>adelantado,</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> </span>sino<span style=''letter-spacing:-.2pt''> </span>únicamente<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>por</span>\r\nperíodos<span style=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span>vencidos<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>QUINTA.</span></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.7pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span></b><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><u style=''text-underline:black''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>INTERÉS<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.55pt''> </span>MORATORIO</span></u></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>.-<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.7pt''> </span></span></b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.15pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>EL ACREDITADO se obliga a pagar a CREA intereses\r\nmoratorios sobre cualquier cantidad vencida y no pagada del crédito<a\r\nname="_Hlk478647289">, a una tasa moratoria igual a multiplicar por un factor\r\nde 2 (dos) veces la tasa de interés ordinaria </a>señalada en la cláusula cuarta\r\nde este contrato. Los intereses moratorios se calcularán multiplicando el saldo\r\nvencido por la tasa de <span class=SpellE>ientrés</span> moratoria efectiva\r\ndesde el día inmediato siguiente de su vencimiento hasta el de su pago total.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.15pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.15pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>En caso de que, conforme a la\r\nLey del Impuesto al Valor Agregado, EL ACREDITADO deba pagar tal impuesto o\r\ncualquier otro que a la fecha se encuentre vigente, deberán ser pagados a CREA conjuntamente\r\ncon los intereses moratorios generados.</span><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>SEXTA.<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.65pt''> </span><u style=''text-underline:black''>COMISIONES</u><u>.-</u><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.7pt''> </span></span></b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Se<span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>le<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>informa<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>al</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.6pt''> </span>ACREDITADO<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.4pt''> </span>que<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>no</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>se<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>cobrará<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>ningún</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>tipo</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>comisión,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>siendo<span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>únicamente<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>los</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:3.9pt;mso-font-width:101%''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>pagos</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.75pt''> </span>descritos<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.75pt''> </span>en las cláusulas cuarta y quinta del\r\npresente contrato.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>SÉPTIMA.</span></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.45pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span></b><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><u style=''text-underline:black''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.15pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>PAGOS</span></u></b><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><u style=''text-underline:black''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.35pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span></u></b><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><u style=''text-underline:black''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>ANTICIPADOS</span></u></b><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><u><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>.-</span></u></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.5pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span></b><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Se <span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt''>entenderán</span> <span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>por</span> <span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>pagos</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>anticipados,</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.05pt''> </span>al<span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>pago</span> <span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>parcial</span>\r\no <span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>total</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.1pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>que</span> <span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>aún</span> <span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>no</span>\r\n<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>es</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>exigible.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Cuando<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.7pt''> </span>lo<span style=''letter-spacing:1.65pt''> </span>solicite<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.7pt''> </span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL\r\nACREDITADO</b>,<span style=''letter-spacing:1.7pt''> </span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''>CREA</b><span style=''letter-spacing:1.7pt''> </span>estará<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.65pt''> </span>obligada<span style=''letter-spacing:1.7pt''>\r\n</span>a<span style=''letter-spacing:1.65pt''> </span>recibir<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.7pt''> </span>pagos anticipados<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.5pt''>. </span></span><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Durante<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>la<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>vigencia<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>del<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>crédito,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL\r\nACREDITADO</b><span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>podrá<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>realizar<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''>\r\n</span>pagos<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>anticipados<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>siempre<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''>\r\n</span>y<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>cuando<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>esté<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>al\r\ncorriente<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.15pt''> </span>sus<span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>pagos<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>exigibles<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.2pt''> </span>y<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>sean<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>por<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>una<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>cantidad<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''>\r\n</span>igual<span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>o<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.15pt''> </span>mayor<span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>al<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>pago<span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>que<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>deba<span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>realizarse<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>el<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>periodo<span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''>\r\n</span>correspondiente.<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>Cuando<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>el importe<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.35pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>los<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>pagos<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>anticipados<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>no<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>fuera<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>suficiente<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.35pt''> </span>para<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>amortizar<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>el<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>saldo<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>insoluto<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''>\r\n</span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>su<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.35pt''> </span>totalidad,<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.35pt''> </span>autoriza<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>a<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>a que<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>disminuya<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>el<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>número<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>pagos<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>a<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>realizar,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>asimismo<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''>\r\n</span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.35pt''> </span>entregará<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>a<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL\r\nACREDITADO</b><span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>una<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>nueva<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>tabla<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>amortización,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>lo<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>anterior\r\ncada vez que <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> anticipe\r\nalgún pago.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>En<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>el</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.0pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>entendido</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.95pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>que</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>el</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.0pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>hecho</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>que</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>anticipe<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>pagos</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.05pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>parciales</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>no</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.85pt''> </span>le<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>exime<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>la<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>obligación</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.95pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>efectuar</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>los<span style=''letter-spacing:1.0pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>pagos</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.9pt''> </span>subsecuentes<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de\r\nacuerdo a la nueva tabla de amortización que CREA entregue a EL\r\nACREDITADO,<span style=''mso-spacerun:yes''>  </span>y que en su momento se <span\r\nclass=SpellE>intergrará</span> como un nuevo anexo al presente contrato.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Para los casos en que existan pagos anticipados,<b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''> CREA</b><span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''>\r\n</span>calculará<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>el<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>importe<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''>\r\n</span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>los<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.15pt''> </span>intereses<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>por<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>devengar,<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.2pt''> </span>con<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>base<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>el<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>nuevo<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>saldo<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>insoluto<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''>\r\n</span>y<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>le<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.1pt''> </span>hará<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>entrega<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>a<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> del comprobante\r\ncorrespondiente al<span style=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span>pago anticipado.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>EL ACREDITADO</span></b><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.55pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>podrá<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.55pt''> </span>hacer<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>pagos<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>totales<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''>\r\n</span>o<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>parciales<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>manera<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>anticipada,<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.55pt''> </span>siempre<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>que<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>estos<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>se<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>realicen<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''>\r\n</span>dentro<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>del<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>horario<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''>\r\n</span>del<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>área<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>Atención<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>a Clientes<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.5pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''>CREA</b>;<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>en<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>caso<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>contrario,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>los<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>recursos<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>se<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>aplicarán<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>el<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>día<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>hábil<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>inmediato<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>siguiente,<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''>\r\n</span>con<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>la<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.5pt''> </span>consecuente<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>actualización<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>de los saldos a pagar.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX;\r\nmso-fareast-language:ES-MX''>En caso que <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL\r\nACREDITADO</b> decida liquidar el crédito de manera anticipada, <b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b> únicamente cobrara el interés\r\nordinario que se haya generado hasta la fecha en que se realice el pago total\r\ndel mismo, más accesorios del crédito que en su caso y de acuerdo a las\r\ncondiciones pactadas mediante éste contrato el crédito se hubiesen generado.</span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>OCTAVA. <u>DE LOS\r\nPAGOS EN EXCESO O INFERIORES A LOS ABONOS</u></span></b><span style=''font-size:\r\n8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>.- En<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>caso<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>que,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>la<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>fecha<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>de<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>pago, <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span>reciba abono<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.05pt''> </span>mayor al<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> </span>establecido\r\nen el presente<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>Contrato,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL\r\nACREDITADO</b><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>podrá<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span>exigir<span style=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''>\r\n</span>el<span style=''letter-spacing:-.2pt''> </span>reembolso<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span>del<span style=''letter-spacing:-.2pt''> </span>pago<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span>exceso<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''> </span>a <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>En<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>caso<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>que,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>la<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>fecha<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>de<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>pago,<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>CREA<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>reciba<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> un\r\n</span>abono<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> por una cantidad </span>menor<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>a la<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>establecida<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>el<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>presente<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>Contrato,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>será responsabilidad de EL ACERDITADO,\r\nrealizar el pago por<span style=''letter-spacing:.85pt''> </span>la<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.85pt''> </span>diferencia<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.85pt''> </span>en el domicilio señalado por CREA para efectos del presente\r\ncontrato.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>NOVENA. <u>ESTADO<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>DE<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>CUENTA.</u>-<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> <span style=''mso-spacerun:yes''> </span></span></span></b><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>De</span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:1.25pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>conformidad<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.25pt''> </span>con<span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>el<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.35pt''> </span>artículo<span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>23</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.2pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.25pt''> </span>la<span style=''letter-spacing:1.35pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>Ley</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.0pt''><span style=''mso-spacerun:yes''> </span>para la </span>Transparencia,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>EL<span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>ACREDITADO<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.25pt''> </span>acepta<span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>realizar</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>la<span style=''letter-spacing:1.2pt''> </span>consulta<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.25pt''> </span>su<span style=''letter-spacing:4.55pt;\r\nmso-font-width:101%''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>estado</span> <span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>de</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>cuenta</span> <span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span>manera<span style=''letter-spacing:1.75pt''>\r\n</span>electrónica<b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''> </b>a través de la\r\npágina </span><span lang=EN-US><a href="http://www.financieracrea.com"><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span lang=ES-MX style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>www.financieracrea.com</span></b></a></span><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> con el Usuario <span\r\nstyle=''mso-spacerun:yes''> </span>y contraseña que ha sido entregado por\r\npersonal facultado por CREA. Así mismo, bajo el consentimiento del presente\r\ncontrato confirma que a la firma del presente instrumento, ha recibido el\r\nusuario y contraseña para poder hacer la consulta del mismo.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>El acreditado <span class=SpellE>esta</span> de\r\nacuerdo y es consciente en cuenta que dicho estado de cuenta puede tardar hasta\r\ndiez días hábiles en mostrar la información referente a un pago <span\r\nclass=SpellE>ú</span> operación.<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> Lo anterior,\r\nderivado del atraso que el patrón pueda tardar en informar a CREA acerca de las\r\nretenciones que se hubiesen realizado a EL ACREDITADO. <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:.5pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>Los<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>estados<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>cuenta<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>contendrán<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.45pt''> </span>al<span style=''letter-spacing:.4pt''> </span>menos<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>lo<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>estipulado<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>el<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>artículo<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''>\r\n</span>35<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.45pt''> </span>las<span style=''letter-spacing:.85pt''> </span>DISPOSICIONES<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.4pt''> </span>DE<span style=''letter-spacing:.4pt''> </span>CARÁCTER<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>GENERAL<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>en<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>materia<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''>\r\n</span>de transparencia<span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>aplicables a<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>las<span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>Sociedades<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>Financieras de<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.25pt''> </span>Objeto Múltiple<span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>Entidades\r\nNo Reguladas.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nletter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>La</span><span style=''font-size:\r\n8.0pt;letter-spacing:.25pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>falta<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.35pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.4pt''> </span>recepción<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>del<span style=''letter-spacing:.4pt''> </span>estado<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>cuenta<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.4pt''> </span>por<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>cualquier<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>circunstancia,<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.4pt''> </span>no<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>libera<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>a<span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.5pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>su</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.4pt''> </span>obligación<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''>\r\n</span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.35pt''> </span>efectuar<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>el</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.3pt''> </span>pago<span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>correspondiente<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:4.2pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>en</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>la fecha<span style=''letter-spacing:-.25pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>límite</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>pago.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><span style=''mso-spacerun:yes''> </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>DÉCIMA.</span></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><u><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.1pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span></u></b><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><u><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>VIGENCIA</span></u></b><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>.-<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.1pt''> </span></span></b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>La</span><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:\r\n.1pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>vigencia<span style=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>del<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> presente contrato,</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.05pt''> </span>será<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>por<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>el<span style=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>plazo<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>estipulado<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>en</span> la<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.15pt''> </span>Carátula<span style=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>del<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span>Contrato<span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''>\r\n</span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>sin</span><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.15pt''> </span>que sea<span style=''letter-spacing:4.9pt''> </span>prorrogable;<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>fecha<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>en<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>la<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>cual<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL\r\nACREDITADO</b><span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>deberá<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>tener<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>cubiertas<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>todas<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>y<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>cada<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>una<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>las<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>obligaciones<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.2pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>pago<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>derivadas<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''>\r\n</span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>este<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.2pt''> </span>Contrato;<span style=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>en<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span>caso contrario,<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.5pt''> </span>el<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>Contrato<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>permanecerá<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.5pt''> </span>vigente<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>hasta<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>tanto<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL\r\nACREDITADO</b><span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>liquide<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>totalmente<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''>\r\n</span>y<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>a<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.5pt''> </span>satisfacción<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>de<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>sus<span style=''letter-spacing:.5pt''> </span>obligaciones\r\nde pago conforme al presente Contrato y al Pagaré.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>DÉCIMA PRIMERA.<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.2pt''> </span><u style=''text-underline:black''>PRELACION<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.05pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>DE</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>LOS<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>PAGOS</span></u><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>.-</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>CREA</span></span></b><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.35pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>aplicará</span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>l