egado, o cualquier otro impuesto que al momento y de\r\nacuerdo a la legislación aplicable se encuentre vigente. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>DÉCIMA SEGUNDA.<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span><u style=''text-underline:black''><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>CESIÓN</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.75pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>DE</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span>DEUDA<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.8pt''> </span>O<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>CRÉDITO</u>.-<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>EL ACREDITADO</span></b><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:1.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>no</span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;letter-spacing:1.05pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>podrá<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.0pt''> </span>ceder<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''>total</span><span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>o<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>parcialmente<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.05pt''> </span>los<span style=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>derechos y obligaciones </span>que<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.05pt''> </span>le <span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>otorga</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.15pt''> </span>el<span style=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>presente<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span>contrato.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p 