e=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>que<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>se<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>relacione<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''>\r\n</span>directamente<span style=''letter-spacing:.85pt''> </span>con<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>la<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>solicitud<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.85pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>aclaración\r\nque<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>corresponda<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>y<span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span>sin\r\nincluir datos correspondientes a operaciones<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>relacionadas\r\ncon terceras<span style=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>personas.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>En<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>todo<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>caso<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b><span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.55pt''> </span>deberá<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>de<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>agotar<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>los<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.55pt''> </span>procedimientos<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.55pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>autenticación<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.45pt''> </span>solicitados<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n.55pt''> </span>por<span style=''letter-spacing:.9pt''> </span><b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b>.<span style=''letter-spacing:.55pt''>\r\n</span>Cualquier aclaración, reclamación o consulta deberá de hacerse por\r\nescrito y<span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''> </span>hacerla llegar a<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.25pt''> </span><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.1pt''> </span>a<span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>su<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>domicilio o por el<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt''> </span>medio que se<span style=''letter-spacing:-.15pt''> </span>le\r\ninstruya.</span><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX''> Asimismo, <b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b> hace del conocimiento de <b\r\nstyle=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL ACREDITADO</b> el número telefónico de\r\natención a usuarios de la Comisión Nacional para la Protección y Defensa de los\r\nUsuarios de Servicios Financieros, para realizar cualquier queja: 5340 0999 ó\r\nLADA sin costo 01800 999 8080, mediante la página www.condusef.gob.mx <span\r\nclass=SpellE>ó</span> mediante el correo electrónico </span><span lang=EN-US><a\r\nhref="mailto:opinion@condusef.gob.mx"><span lang=ES-MX style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX;mso-fareast-language:\r\nES-MX''>opinion@condusef.gob.mx</span></a></span><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX;\r\nmso-fareast-language:ES-MX''>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>VIGÉSIMA.<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.15pt''> </span><u style=''text-underline:black''>TITULO<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:.85pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>EJECUTIVO</span></u><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>.-</span><span style=''letter-spacing:.95pt''> </span></span></b><span\r\nstyle=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>En<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.1pt''> </span>términos<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>del<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>artículo<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''>\r\n</span>68<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.1pt''> </span>la<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>Ley<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>instituciones<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>Crédito,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>el<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>presente<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>Contrato<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''>\r\n</span>junto<span style=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>con<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.1pt''> </span>el Estado de Cuenta certificado expedido por\r\nel Contador debidamente autorizado por <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>CREA</b>,\r\nserá título ejecutivo sin necesidad de reconocimiento de<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.85pt''> </span>firma<span style=''letter-spacing:1.85pt''> </span>o<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:1.85pt''> </span>cualquier<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span>otro<span style=''letter-spacing:1.85pt''> </span>requisito,<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span>por<span style=''letter-spacing:1.85pt''> </span>lo<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span>que,<span style=''letter-spacing:1.85pt''> </span>en<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span>caso<span style=''letter-spacing:1.85pt''> </span>de<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span>incumplimiento<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.85pt''> </span>por<span style=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span>parte<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.85pt''> </span>de <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:normal''>EL\r\nACREDITADO</b><span style=''letter-spacing:1.85pt''> </span>o<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span>en<span style=''letter-spacing:1.85pt''> </span>caso<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span>de<span style=''letter-spacing:1.85pt''> </span>vencimiento<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''> </span>anticipado, <b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''>CREA</b> estará facultado para demandar en la vía ejecutiva<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:2.2pt''> </span>mercantil o en la vía que más le convenga.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ES-MX''><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=''text-align:justify''><b style=''mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal''><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX''>VIGÉSIMA<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.8pt''> </span>PRIMERA.<span style=''letter-spacing:1.9pt''>\r\n</span><u style=''text-underline:black''>MODIFICACIONES.-<span style=''letter-spacing:\r\n1.9pt''> </span></u></span></b><span style=''font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nES-MX''>Ninguna<span style=''letter-spacing:1.8pt''> </span>modificación<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.8pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>de</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.6pt''> </span><span style=''letter-spacing:-.05pt''>término</span><span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.8pt''> </span>o<span style=''letter-spacing:1.8pt''> </span>condición<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.8pt''> </span>alguna<span style=''letter-spacing:1.75pt''>\r\n</span>del<span style=''letter-spacing:1.85pt''> </span>presente<span\r\nstyle=''letter-spacing:1.8pt''> </span>Contrato,<span style=''letter-spacing:1.7pt''>\r\n</span>y<span style=''letter-spacing:4.75pt;mso-font-width:101%''> </span><span\r\nstyle=''lett